  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2950757">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2950757/" class="title-link">萨特以及他的存在主义</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2950757"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/lipan/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1320858-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lipan/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">黎盼</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-01-23"
      class="main-meta">2010-01-23 17:19:02</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2950757_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  最早听说萨特，是在高中的语文读本上，一篇名为《墙》的小说，使我对这个世界的荒诞以及啼笑皆非印象深刻。后来，上大学后对于萨特其人，及其存在主义听到得越来越多，越来越好奇。在学校的图书馆里，能找到的关于萨特的书并不多，其实就是整个跟文学沾得上边的书也不多，三楼...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2950757/#comments">(11回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">26有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
